AddlName1.title: Additional Name
AddlName1.description: An additional name that can be associated with the structured names that appear in the individual entity. The structure consists of a generic proper name with associated type example Name - Smith Name Type Code: Father Surname Name - Park Name Type Code: Mother Surname

individual.title: Each Additional Name may have one and only one Individual
individual.description: A single human being as distinct from a group, class, or family.

name.title: Additional Name.Name
name.description: A proper additional name is defined by the associated name type code and further clarified by the description text. Name - Smith Name Type Code: Father Surname Name - Park Name Type Code: Mother Surname

nameTypeCode.title: Additional Name.Name Type Code
nameTypeCode.description: The type of proper name Examples Father Surname Mother Surname

description.example: An apple mobile which is nothing like apple
